    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines Seamless Bidirectional Forwarding Detection (S-BFD), a simplified mechanism for using BFD with a large proportion of negotiation aspects eliminated, thus providing benefits such as quick provisioning, as well as improved control and flexibility for network nodes initiating path monitoring.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This document updates RFC 5880.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
